706797f-b.text:
(1)

Sidney Place, North from State Street. In the back-
ground is seen the steeple of St. Charles Borromeo R.C. Church.

October 1928.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

(2)
The same, further north on Sidney Place.
February 22, 1930.
F.L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

(3)
The same, showing the same view at a later date.
June 1, 1934.

F.L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
